Package: econ
Type: Package
Title: Econometrics
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-03-23
Author: Stuart Baumann [aut, cre], Margaryta Klymak[ctb]
Maintainer: Stuart Baumann <Stuart.Baumann@ed.ac.uk>
Description: There exist many econometrics package on CRAN. These
	packages lack a consistent syntax and furthermore offer too
	many options for many users. The purpose of this package is 
	to provide simple and consistent access to most of the 
	functions that are regularly used in econometrics.
License:  MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
Imports: sandwich, stargazer, lmtest, aod
Suggests: knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
